---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<section class="hero">
				<h1>用「精聽」真正聽懂英文</h1>
				<p class="subtitle">
					大量聽不等於聽懂。SubFit Blog 分享沉浸式英文訓練的核心技巧——精聽方法、工具評比、學習心法——幫助你從「聽到」進化到「聽懂」。
				</p>
				<a href="https://subfit.vercel.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta-btn">
					立即體驗 SubFit App →
				</a>
			</section>

			<section class="features">
				<div class="feature">
					<div class="feature-icon">🎧</div>
					<h2>精聽技巧</h2>
					<p>不只是「多聽」，而是有策略地聽。學習如何用影片字幕做精聽練習，訓練真實語境的聽力。</p>
				</div>
				<div class="feature">
					<div class="feature-icon">🛠️</div>
					<h2>工具評比</h2>
					<p>比較各種沉浸式學習工具的優缺點，找到最適合自己學習節奏的組合。</p>
				</div>
				<div class="feature">
					<div class="feature-icon">🧠</div>
					<h2>學習心法</h2>
					<p>從語言習得研究出發，建立正確的學習觀念，避免常見陷阱，讓時間花在刀口上。</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="latest">
				<h2>最新文章</h2>
				<a href="/blog" class="blog-link">前往文章列表 →</a>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	main {
		max-width: 720px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 2em 1em;
	}

	.hero {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 3em 1em 2em;
	}

	.hero h1 {
		font-size: 2.4em;
		margin-bottom: 0.5em;
		line-height: 1.2;
	}

	.subtitle {
		font-size: 1.1em;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		max-width: 520px;
		margin: 0 auto 2em;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.cta-btn {
		display: inline-block;
		background: rgb(99, 102, 241);
		color: white;
		padding: 0.75em 1.8em;
		border-radius: 8px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: bold;
		font-size: 1em;
		transition: background 0.2s;
	}

	.cta-btn:hover {
		background: rgb(79, 82, 221);
	}

	.features {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5em;
		margin: 3em 0;
	}

	.feature {
		padding: 1.5em;
		background: rgba(var(--gray-light), 0.3);
		border-radius: 10px;
	}

	.feature-icon {
		font-size: 1.8em;
		margin-bottom: 0.4em;
	}

	.feature h2 {
		font-size: 1.1em;
		margin: 0 0 0.5em;
	}

	.feature p {
		font-size: 0.9em;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.latest {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: space-between;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(var(--gray-light), 0.5);
		padding-top: 2em;
		margin-top: 1em;
	}

	.latest h2 {
		margin: 0;
	}

	.blog-link {
		color: rgb(99, 102, 241);
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: bold;
	}

	.blog-link:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}
</style>
